  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/26174818/when-default-methods-will-be-supported-java-8-in-android",
  "title" : "When default methods will be supported (Java 8) in Android?",
  "body" : "<p>I was wondering if I can use default methods in interfaces in Android development.\nThe feature is included in Java 8, but I have found out that Android Java VM doesn't yet support it.\nIt there any way to use default methods in Android development? If not, when this feature will be available, is there some kind of timeline for this features?</p>\n"
